article.description: — Trey Anderson had 17 points and eight rebounds and Omari Moore posted 13 points and seven assists as San Jose State rolled past North Dakota 76-51 on Friday night.
article.headline: Anderson carries San Jose St. over North Dakota 76-51
article.linkText: Anderson carries San Jose St. over North Dakota 76-51
article.story: SAN JOSE, Calif. -- — Trey Anderson had 17 points and eight rebounds and Omari Moore posted 13 points and seven assists as San Jose State rolled past North Dakota 76-51 on Friday night. Trey Smith had 17 points for San Jose State (4-3), which earned its fourth straight home victory. Alvaro Cardenas Torre added 10 points.
